text: Trichordestra lilacina, the aster cutworm, is a species of cutworm or dart moth in the family Noctuidae. It is found in North America. The MONA or Hodges number for Trichordestra lilacina is 10307. ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * Category:Hadenini Category:Moths described in 1874
